{
  "info": {
    "name": "Krypton E-commerce — Órdenes / Checkout",
    "description": "Checkout, ciclo de vida de órdenes y pago simulado de Krypton.\n\nFlujo sugerido:\n1. Corrés 'Login (admin)' → guarda {{adminToken}}.\n2. Creás categoría y producto de prueba.\n3. Registrás un cliente y hacés 'Login (cliente)' → guarda {{clientToken}}.\n4. Agregás un ítem al carrito (prerequisito del checkout).\n5. Hacés checkout → se crea la orden en PENDIENTE, guarda {{orderId}}.\n6. Simulás el pago → la orden pasa a CONFIRMADA.\n7. El admin puede ver todas las órdenes y cambiar el estado a cualquier valor.\n\nBase URL por defecto: http://localhost:8080\nAdmin sembrado: admin@krypton.pe / Admin123!\n\nNotas de comportamiento:\n- Checkout es atómico: si el stock no alcanza para algún ítem, no se crea nada (rollback completo).\n- El precio se congela al momento del checkout (price snapshot) — cambios futuros no afectan la orden.\n- Solo se puede pagar una orden en PENDIENTE → 422 si ya está CONFIRMADA o CANCELADA.\n- IDOR: un cliente no puede ver ni pagar la orden de otro usuario (→ 404).\n- El admin puede transicionar a cualquier estado sin restricciones.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    { "key": "baseUrl",        "value": "http://localhost:8080" },
    { "key": "adminToken",     "value": "" },
    { "key": "clientToken",    "value": "" },
    { "key": "adminEmail",     "value": "admin@krypton.pe" },
    { "key": "adminPassword",  "value": "Admin123!" },
    { "key": "clientEmail",    "value": "cliente@test.pe" },
    { "key": "clientPassword", "value": "Cliente123!" },
    { "key": "categoryId",     "value": "1" },
    { "key": "productId",      "value": "1" },
    { "key": "orderId",        "value": "1" }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Setup — Datos de prueba",
      "description": "Preparación: tokens, categoría, producto y carrito listo para checkout. Corré en orden la primera vez.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "1. Login (admin) → guarda adminToken",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "const res = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (res.token) {",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('adminToken', res.token);",
                  "  console.log('adminToken guardado');",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api", "auth", "login"] },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"{{adminEmail}}\",\n  \"password\": \"{{adminPassword}}\"\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "2. Create category → guarda categoryId",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "const res = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (res.id) {",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('categoryId', res.id);",
                  "  console.log('categoryId =', res.id);",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type",  "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{adminToken}}" }
            ],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/admin/categories", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api", "admin", "categories"] },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"Laptops\",\n  \"description\": \"Notebooks y ultrabooks\"\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "description": "Si ya existe (409), editá el nombre o saltea este paso y ajustá {{categoryId}} manualmente."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "3. Create product → guarda productId",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "const res = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (res.id) {",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('productId', res.id);",
                  "  console.log('productId =', res.id);",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type",  "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{adminToken}}" }
            ],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/admin/products", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api", "admin", "products"] },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"sku\": \"LAP-ORD-01\",\n  \"name\": \"Notebook Krypton 14\",\n  \"description\": \"Core i5, 16GB RAM, 512GB SSD\",\n  \"price\": 2999.90,\n  \"stock\": 10,\n  \"imageUrl\": \"https://example.com/lap-ord-01.jpg\",\n  \"categoryId\": {{categoryId}}\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "description": "Crea el producto con stock=10. El precio quedará congelado en la orden al momento del checkout."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "4. Register (cliente)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api", "auth", "register"] },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"Cliente Tester\",\n  \"email\": \"{{clientEmail}}\",\n  \"password\": \"{{clientPassword}}\"\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "description": "201 si es nuevo, 409 si ya existe (saltá este paso en ese caso)."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "5. Login (cliente) → guarda clientToken",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "const res = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (res.token) {",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('clientToken', res.token);",
                  "  console.log('clientToken guardado');",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api", "auth", "login"] },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"{{clientEmail}}\",\n  \"password\": \"{{clientPassword}}\"\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "6. Add item to cart (prerequisito checkout)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type",  "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{clientToken}}" }
            ],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/cart/items", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api", "cart", "items"] },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"productId\": {{productId}},\n  \"quantity\": 2\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "description": "Agrega 2 unidades al carrito. El checkout va a consumir este carrito y vaciarlo."
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Checkout & Órdenes (cliente)",
      "description": "Checkout atómico, consulta de historial y pago simulado. Todos requieren {{clientToken}}.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "POST /api/orders/checkout → guarda orderId",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "const res = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (res.id) {",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('orderId', res.id);",
                  "  console.log('orderId =', res.id, '| status =', res.status, '| total =', res.total);",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{clientToken}}" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/orders/checkout", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api", "orders", "checkout"] },
            "description": "Convierte el carrito en una orden. Transacción única: valida stock → crea Order (PENDIENTE) → snapshot de precio → descuenta stock → registra movimientos → vacía el carrito. 201 OrderResponse. 400 si el carrito está vacío. 422 si el stock no alcanza."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "GET /api/orders — mi historial",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{clientToken}}" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/orders", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api", "orders"] },
            "description": "Devuelve todas las órdenes del cliente autenticado, ordenadas por fecha DESC. Solo sus propias órdenes."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "GET /api/orders/{{orderId}} — detalle de mi orden",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{clientToken}}" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/orders/{{orderId}}", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api", "orders", "{{orderId}}"] },
            "description": "Detalle de la orden {{orderId}}. 404 si no existe o pertenece a otro usuario (IDOR). Verificar que unit_price refleja el precio al momento del checkout, no el precio actual."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "POST /api/orders/{{orderId}}/pay — pago simulado",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type",  "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{clientToken}}" }
            ],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/orders/{{orderId}}/pay", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api", "orders", "{{orderId}}", "pay"] },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"method\": \"CREDIT_CARD\"\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "description": "Simula el pago. Transiciona la orden de PENDIENTE → CONFIRMADA. method acepta: CREDIT_CARD, YAPE, EFECTIVO. 200 OrderResponse con status=CONFIRMADA. 422 si la orden ya está CONFIRMADA o CANCELADA. 404 si la orden no es del cliente autenticado."
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Admin — Órdenes (requiere adminToken)",
      "description": "Gestión de todas las órdenes del sistema. Requiere rol ADMIN ({{adminToken}}).",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "GET /api/admin/orders — todas las órdenes (paginado)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{adminToken}}" }],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/admin/orders?page=0&size=20&sort=orderDate,desc",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "admin", "orders"],
              "query": [
                { "key": "page", "value": "0" },
                { "key": "size", "value": "20" },
                { "key": "sort", "value": "orderDate,desc" }
              ]
            },
            "description": "Lista paginada de TODAS las órdenes del sistema. Cada OrderResponse incluye userId para identificar al cliente. 403 si el token es de CLIENTE."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "GET /api/admin/orders/{{orderId}} — detalle (cualquier usuario)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{adminToken}}" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/admin/orders/{{orderId}}", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api", "admin", "orders", "{{orderId}}"] },
            "description": "Detalle de cualquier orden sin restricción de propietario. 404 si la orden no existe."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "PUT /api/admin/orders/{{orderId}}/status — CONFIRMADA",
          "request": {
            "method": "PUT",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type",  "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{adminToken}}" }
            ],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/admin/orders/{{orderId}}/status", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api", "admin", "orders", "{{orderId}}", "status"] },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"status\": \"CONFIRMADA\"\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "description": "El admin puede transicionar a cualquier estado sin restricciones. Valores válidos: PENDIENTE, CONFIRMADA, CANCELADA. 200 OrderResponse actualizado."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "PUT /api/admin/orders/{{orderId}}/status — CANCELADA",
          "request": {
            "method": "PUT",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type",  "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{adminToken}}" }
            ],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/admin/orders/{{orderId}}/status", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api", "admin", "orders", "{{orderId}}", "status"] },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"status\": \"CANCELADA\"\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "description": "Cancela la orden. El admin puede cancelar incluso órdenes CONFIRMADAS — sin restricción de transición."
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Casos de error",
      "description": "Validaciones, guards y IDOR del checkout y órdenes.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "400 — checkout con carrito vacío",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{clientToken}}" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/orders/checkout", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api", "orders", "checkout"] },
            "description": "El carrito ya fue vaciado por el checkout anterior. Debe responder 400 EmptyCartException. (Si el carrito tiene ítems, primero hacé DELETE /api/cart para vaciarlo.)"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "422 — pagar una orden ya CONFIRMADA",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type",  "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{clientToken}}" }
            ],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/orders/{{orderId}}/pay", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api", "orders", "{{orderId}}", "pay"] },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"method\": \"YAPE\"\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "description": "La orden {{orderId}} ya fue pagada (CONFIRMADA). Debe responder 422 OrderStatusTransitionException."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "404 — IDOR: admin intenta pagar orden del cliente",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type",  "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{adminToken}}" }
            ],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/orders/{{orderId}}/pay", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api", "orders", "{{orderId}}", "pay"] },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"method\": \"EFECTIVO\"\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "description": "La orden {{orderId}} pertenece al cliente, no al admin. Debe responder 404 — no se revela que la orden existe (IDOR protection)."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "401 — sin token",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/orders/checkout", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api", "orders", "checkout"] },
            "description": "Sin Authorization header. Debe responder 401."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "403 — cliente accede a endpoint admin",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{clientToken}}" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/admin/orders", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api", "admin", "orders"] },
            "description": "Token de CLIENTE en endpoint de ADMIN. Debe responder 403 Forbidden."
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
